[30/07, 4:10 pm] Ajit: Authentication flow diagram
[30/07, 4:10 pm] Ajit: User          Client Application          Authentication Server
 |                   |                            |
 |--- Access Protected Resource --->              |
 |                   |                            |
 |<--- Redirect to Login Page -----               |
 |                   |                            |
 |--- Show Login Page (JSP) --->                  |
 |                   |                            |
 |<--- Enter Credentials --------                 |
 |                   |                            |
 |--- POST /login with credentials --->           |
 |                   |                            |
 |                 Validate                      |
 |                   |                            |
 |<--- Issue JWT Token ---------                 |
 |                   |                            |
 |--- Redirect to Original Resource with Token--> |
 |                   |                            |
 |--- Access Protected Resource with Token --->   |
 |                   |                            |
 |                 Validate                      |
 |                   |                            |
 |<--- Allow Access to Resource ---               |
