[30/07, 4:11 pm] Ajit: Sequence diagram for login
[30/07, 4:11 pm] Ajit: User                Client App               Auth Server
 |                     |                         |
 |--- Access Login Page -->                     |
 |                     |                         |
 |<--- Show Login Form ---                      |
 |                     |                         |
 |--- Submit Login Form -->                     |
 |                     |                         |
 |                     |--- Validate Credentials -->|
 |                     |                         |
 |                     |<--- Issue JWT Token ---- |
 |                     |                         |
 |<--- Redirect with Token ---                   |
 |                     |                         |
 |--- Access Resource with Token -->            |
 |                     |                         |
 |                     |--- Validate Token -->   |
 |                     |                         |
 |                     |<--- Token Valid --------|
 |<--- Access Granted ---                        |
